OL,4,Cabusing boys at Catholic boarding
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FA "sinister" monk who admitted having
OL,8,F"crushes" on adolescent boys has been
OL,9,Ffound guilty of sexually abusing two
OL,10,Fpupils at a prestigious Catholic
OL,11,Fboarding school.
OL,13,FMichael James Callaghan, known as
OL,14,FFather James, preyed on teenage boys
OL,15,Fwho were "isolated from their
OL,16,Ffamilies" while he was a teacher and
OL,17,Fhousemaster at Ampleforth College in
OL,18,FNorth Yorkshire.
