OL,7,FTeesside Crown Court heard that
OL,8,FCallaghan, now 71, groomed and
OL,9,Frepeatedly indecently assaulted one
OL,10,Fboy over three years in the 1990s, and
OL,11,Fsexually assaulted a 17-year-old in
OL,12,F2013 by squeezing his bottom during a
OL,13,Fhug.
OL,15,FJurors were told he "ingratiated
OL,16,Fhimself" with the first complainant by
OL,17,Fgiving him cigarettes, buying him
OL,18,Fgifts and taking him out shopping and
OL,19,Ffor pub lunches in the North York
OL,20,FMoors.
