OL,7,FThe complainant told police the
OL,8,F"sexual bit" of their relationship had
OL,9,Fstarted when he was under 16, with
OL,10,FCallaghan kissing him.
OL,12,FHe said Callaghan would ask to meet
OL,13,Fhim after Mass on Saturday evenings at
OL,14,Fdifferent locations, including guest
OL,15,Frooms, and sometimes a room at the
OL,16,Fschool that was used for homeless
OL,17,Fpeople.
