OL,7,FThe complainant said in his police
OL,8,Finterview that Callaghan would "take
OL,9,Fon the role of a boy I had a crush on"
OL,10,Fand they would kiss and simulate sex,
OL,11,Ftelling officers he "hated the sexual
OL,12,Fbit of it" and realised as an adult it
OL,13,F"wasn't right".
OL,15,FHe told police: "He had been grooming
OL,16,Fme for three years. There's a
OL,17,Fdifference between welcoming someone's
OL,18,Faffections and the other things that
OL,19,Fwere going on in that room."
