OL,7,FThe defendant admitted having some
OL,8,Fsexual contact with the boy but
OL,9,Fclaimed it was consensual and only
OL,10,Fafter he turned 16, telling jurors the
OL,11,Frelationship was "unusual but not
OL,12,Fcriminal".
OL,14,FBut the prosecution said it "was not
OL,15,Fconsent given freely by someone who
OL,16,Fhad a real choice".
OL,18,FIn his closing speech to jurors,
OL,19,Fprosecutors Mark McKone KC said: "The
OL,20,Fdefendant is massively watering down
OL,21,Fwhat he did.
