OL,7,FThe trial heard that Callaghan had
OL,8,Fconfessed to a doctor in 1990 that he
OL,9,Fhad "crushes" on "a number of boys" at
OL,10,Fa previous school, but "by and large
OL,11,Fhad managed to control himself".
OL,13,FA letter from the doctor said: "When I
OL,14,Ffirst saw him he was rushing after
OL,15,Fadolescent boys he saw in the street."
OL,17,FThe court was told Callaghan went to
OL,18,Fsee the same doctor again in 1993 and
OL,19,Fsaid he was having "more difficulty in
OL,20,Fcontrolling the sexual side of his
OL,21,Flife".
